The '''Kessel prison''', also the '''Imperial Correctional Facility''', was a [[Prison/Legends|prison]] created to keep various people who were dangerous to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] locked away. Later, there was a revolt, and a prison employee named [[Moruth Doole]], a [[Rybet/Legends|Rybet]], took it over and forced former Imperial guards to work in the spice mines of Kessel. He employed the former prisoners as his own personal guards.

[[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] was shot down and captured during the [[assault on Kile II]]. He traveled by [[armored hovertrain]] to the prison, but was [[Rescue on Kessel|released]] by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] before arriving there.

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] were on a diplomatic trip to [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]] when they were captured by Doole and forced to work in the spice mine. They escaped with the help of [[Kyp Durron]].

